goodnight , vienna ( also known as magic night ) is a 1932 british musical film directed by herbert wilcox and starring jack buchanan , anna neagle and gina malo .   two lovers in vienna are separated by the first world war , but are later reunited .   it was based on a radio operetta written by eric maschwitz .   it features the song " good-night , vienna " .   wilcox reportedly cast neagle , whom he would later marry and direct in many films , after discovering her by chance in a stage show .